      C6[结果能否改写 state?]
      C1 ~~~ C2 ~~~ C3 ~~~ C4 ~~~ C5 ~~~ C6
    end

    style TL fill:#fdeeee,stroke:#c0392b,stroke-width:1.5px
    style CR fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:1.5px
